      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS to produce a distinct, metallic exhaust note and linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M Variable Differential Lock for optimal traction. Recent preventative maintenance includes a cooling system overhaul and a comprehensive rear subframe inspection. While the exterior and interior show minor patina expected of a well-loved driver, the performance remains sharp with crisp turn-in and excellent throttle response. A quintessential driver's specification for the purist.",
